{
  "stem": "25423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he used to go the superior and say, I think that Roman has to help me today in the apiary because you want to extract honey.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I used to come there, he used to cut, you see, a honeycomb out of there-- off their beehive and give it to me, and so I could enjoy some honey, which did a great deal for my soul.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my depression was dissipated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I went to the mother house, and they didn't know that I'm Jewish, and they assumed that I'm a novice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they exposed me to the training of a novice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to sit on my knees for two, three hours and listen to singing-- which was totally alien-- and participate in all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought I would go mad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until I started to adapt to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Second point, I was perpetually hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because food was brought and served-- there was a huge table in the refectory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was roughly 80 monks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And first, the abbot used to get-- was served, and then down the road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the novices were at the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So usually, the abbot used to knock, it's time to go back to prayers and to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So when food came to the novices, we had no time to eat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's part and parcel of the training.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Across the border, actually, singing in the funeral of a peasant because you wouldn't cross the border at the demarcation line easily.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So a peasant died in the village, but the cemetery was in Soviet Union, but he lived in Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went with the priest from Rawa Ruska to participate in the funeral.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I sung at-- as a cantor, which I'm trained, by the way, with the funeral.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
